# Connected Sources (via MCPs + CLIs)

| Source | MCP | When to use |
|--------|-----|-------------|
| Obsidian Vault | Read/Write/Grep + ob-smart-connections | ALWAYS, source of truth |
| Notion | `mcp__notion__*` (plugin) + `notionApi` (settings.json) | Tasks, databases |
| MS Calendar | microsoft-graph-mcp | Work meetings, agenda |
| Teams Chats | microsoft-graph-mcp | Work context, decisions |
| Outlook | microsoft-graph-mcp | Work communications (FILTER spam/sales) |
| Read.AI | read-ai MCP | Meeting transcriptions |
| Google Calendar | gcal MCP | Personal/secondary agenda |
| Gmail | gmail MCP | Personal emails |
| iMessages | iMessages MCP | Personal communications |
| GitHub | `gh` CLI | Code, projects |
| Apple Notes | Apple Notes MCP | Quick notes, mobile capture |
| YouTube / 1800+ sites | yt-dlp (CLI) | Subtitles, metadata, transcripts |
| RSS/Atom feeds | feedparser (Python lib) | News feeds, blogs |
| Twitter/X | bird CLI (cookies) | Search, read, timeline, threads |
| LinkedIn | linkedin-scraper-mcp (MCP) | Profiles, companies, jobs, search |
| draw.io | drawio MCP (HTTP, mcp.draw.io/mcp) | Interactive inline diagrams |
| Figma | Figma MCP (plugin) | Design context, screenshots, Code Connect |

## Cross-referencing Rules

- **Work context**: Teams + Outlook + MS Calendar + Read.AI + Notion + vault `10-Work/`
- **People context**: vault `70-People/` + iMessages + Gmail + Teams + LinkedIn
- **Meetings context**: Read.AI + Google Cal + MS Calendar + vault Meetings/
- **Content context**: vault `30-Content/` + Notion ideas + Gmail + Twitter + YouTube

## Known Issues

### Notion MCP
- If using multiple Notion MCPs (e.g., plugin + legacy notionApi), they may access different database copies.
- **Task database ID:** `{{NOTION_DB_ID}}`
- Track which MCP has access to your real database vs. copies.
- Status property values vary by setup (e.g., `Done`, `Ongoing`, `In Progress`).

### MCP Scoping
- **Global** (`~/.claude/settings.json`): filesystem, memory, sequential-thinking
- **Project** (`.mcp.json`): microsoft-graph, notionApi, playwright
- **User-scope** (`claude mcp add --scope user`): linkedin, ob-smart-connections, read-ai
- Adjust scoping based on which MCPs you need globally vs. per-project.

### Microsoft Graph
- Server path: `{{MS_GRAPH_PATH}}`
- Token expires in long sessions (~1h). If you get 401/403 on Teams/Outlook/Calendar: token expired. Workaround: restart session or re-auth.
- Calendars.ReadWrite is active (POST to create events). Created events are always personal.

### Email Filtering
- SKIP emails from spam, cold outreach, sales. Criteria: generic sales subject, unknown sender with no prior context, unsolicited newsletters.
